onwongo tye cok ki ngeye. Gu kato ki i dukan me cato buk ki dukan me wer,
ot cam ma ki lwongo ni hamburger ki ot mogo ma ki neno iye filim, ento pe tye kama nen calo ki twero cato ne
in itye gin ma ki lwongo ni magic wand. Man onwongo obedo gudu ma opong ki dano ma rwate.
Tika twero bedo ni tye dul jabu ma ki yiko mairo mapol piny gi? Onwongo tye kunu
ada dukan ma gi cato buk me leb ki jami ma ki lwongo ni broomsticks? Man pe twero bedo gin mo
lok me yom cwiny madit ma jo me ot pa Dursley gu yubu? Ka onongo Harry pe ngeyo ni
