Dwe me agiki pa H arry ki jo me ot pa Dursleys pi obedo me yomcwiny. Adaa, Dudley onwongo dong tye kit meno
ki lworo i kom Harry en onongo pe obi bedo i ot acel, ma Aunt Petunia ki
Nera Vernon pi oketo Harry i kabad ne, odiyo en me timo gin mo keken, onyo
koko i kome — adaa, gin pi gu lok kwede wacel. Nucu lworo, nucu
ki akemo, gu timo calo kom mo keken ma tye ki Harry iye tye nono. Ma kadi
