Got pa latim tango
DUL KWAN ME APAR
HALLOWEEN
M alfoy pi twero ye gin ma en oneno i kare ma oneno ni Harry ki Ron onongo pud gitye
i Hogwarts nino ma lubo, nen calo olo ento yom cwiny. Adaa, ki
odiko ma lubo Harry ki Ron gutamo ni rwate ki gwok ma tye ki wic adek ni
obedo gin maber atika, ki onongo gi mito bedo ki mukene. Iye
i kare meno, Harry oloko bot Ron lok i kom gin ma onongo nen calo tye
gu aa ki i Gringotts me cito i Hogwarts, ki gu tero kare malac me tamo ngo ma
twero bedo ni mito gwok ma tek kit meno.
"Tye gin ma pire tek onyo rac atika," Ron owaco.
"Onyo gin weng," Harry owaco.
Ento kit ma gin onongo gingeyo maber i kom gin ma pe wangeyo ni onongo tye
ma romo inci aryo, onongo pe gitye ki kare me byeko ngo ma onongo tye
labongo ngec mukene.
Neville ki Hermione pe gu nyutu miti mo keken i kom ngo ma tye ka time
piny pa gwok ki doggola ma ki mako iye. Gin ma Neville onongo paro iye ni pe obi cito
cok ki gwok ni.
Hermione onongo dong tye ka kwero lok ki Harry ki Ron, ento en onongo tye kit meno
ladit ma ngeyo jami weng ni gineno man calo gin ma ki medo. Gin ma onongo gimito
kombedi onwongo obedo yoo me dwogo cen bot Malfoy, ki pi yom cwiny gi madit, kit meno
gin ni oo i mail i nge cabit acel.
Kit ma ler ma ki lwongo ni owls ni opong i ot madit ni calo kare weny, dano weng gu keto cwiny gi i kom
ki mako cut cut ki gin mabor, ma tidi ma ki tingo ki winyo abicel madongo.
Harry onwongo tye ki miti calo dano weng me neno ngo ma tye i kin jami ma dit ni,
ki obedo ki awura i kare ma ler ma ki lwongo ni owls ni gupoto piny ki gubolo piny i nyime,
goyo ringo ringo ne piny i ngom. Gin onongo pwod pe gu kato woko ki i yoo ma
ler mukene obolo waraga i kom gin ma ki cwalo ni.
Harry oyabo waraga ni mukwongo, ma onwongo ber, pien onwongo waco ni:
PE I YAB PARCEL MA I MEJ.
