Onwongo obedo gin marac atika. Fut apar wiye aryo, del kome onwongo nen macol, macol,
kome madit ma nen calo got ma dit ki wiye ma tidi ma yer wic ma ocung i wiye calo
kokonat. Onwongo tye ki tyene ma cok ma pek calo yat ki tyene ma rwate, ma nen calo tyene. Ngwec ne
aa ki iye onwongo ber atika. Onwongo tye ka mako gin ma ki yubu ki bao, ma
ki tingo i ngom pien cinge onwongo boco.
Laco ni ocung i nget doggola ki oneno iye. Owoto mabor
it, ma tye ka moko tam ne matidi ni, ki odonyo mot mot i ot.
"Lagony ma tye i dog ot," Harry owaco ki dwan malongo. "Wa twero umu ne iye."
"Tam maber," Ron owaco ki lworo.
Gu cito tung bot doggola ma oyabe, dog gi otwo, kun gi lega ni lakwo ni pe
cok kato woko ki iye. Ki ngwec acel madit, Harry omako ki ma ki lwongo ni,
turo doggola ni, ki lok ne.
"Ee!"
Pi bedo ki lworo i kom loyo lweny gi, oyabo ngwec cen malo i yoo, ento ma calo
gu oo i but piny gu winyo gin mo ma oweko cwiny gi ocung matek — a
koko ma malo, ma opong ki lworo — ki onwongo tye ka aa ki i ot ma onwongo gi tye iye
ki tweyo ki nyor.
