Got pa latim tango
DUL ME ARYO
Kiyo pa ERISED
Karama onwongo tye ka bino. I odiko mo acel i kine ka dwe me apar wiye aryo, Hogwarts oya ki
nongo kome ki umu ki pee ma romo fut mapol. Nam ni odoko ngiic matek ki Weasley
lutino rudi ki pwodo gi pi tic ki jami ma ki lwongo ni snowballs mapol wek gu lubo
Quirrell orumo, kun ngweco ki i nge bongo ne. Owinyo manok ma gu twero
me lweny i kin polo ma tye ka cwer matek me cwalo waraga onongo myero ki dwoko cen
me yotkom pa Hagrid ma peya gu twero ngwec cen.
Pe tye ngat mo ma twero kuru nino madito me cako. I kare ma Gryffindor
ot ma dano gibedo iye ki ot madit ni onongo tye ki mac ma lyel, ki yoo ma yamo mol iye onongo tye ki
odoko pee ki yamo magwar obalo wang ot ma i ot kwan. Marac loyo weng
onwongo tye i kilaci pa lapwony Snape piny i ot mabuc, kama yweyo gi oya iye
buru ma tye i nyimgi ki gu bedo cok ki jami gi ma lyet.
"Cwinya cwer tutwal," owaco Draco Malfoy, ngat acel i kilaci me Potions, "pi jo eni weng
dano ma omyera gubed i Hogwarts pi Karama pien pe ki miito gi
i gang.
En onwongo tye ka neno Harry ma en tye ka lok. Crabbe ki Goyle gubedo ka nyero.
Harry, ma onwongo tye ka pimo ler ma ki lwongo ni lionfish, okwero gi. Malfoy
onwongo tye marac makato ma onwongo tye i tuku me Quidditch. Cwero cwinye
ma Slytherins gu rwenyo, en otemo miyo dano weny gi nyero kit ma ler ma ki lwongo ni widedoed tree frog obi bedo ka loko Harry ma calo Seeker ma lubo. En oniang ni
ni ngat mo pe onongo ni lok man yomo yic, pien gin weng gubedo ki ur i kom kit ma
Harry otemo bedo i kom yat ma ki lwongo ni bucking broomstick. Pi meno Malfoy, jemo ki
ki akemo, odok cen ka buru Harry pi bedo ki jo me ode ma opore.
Onwongo tye lok ada ni Harry onwongo pe tye ka dok cen i Privet Drive pi Karama.
Lapwony McGonagall onwongo obino cabit ma okato, kun yubu lok ma mako
lutino kwan ma gubi bedo pi kare me yweyo, ki Harry onwongo ocoyo nyinge i
icel. En pe owinyo marac pi kome kekene wacel; man twero bedo gin maber loyo
Karama ma en onongo pwod peya obedo kwede. Ron ki omegine onongo gitye ka bedo, bene, pien Mr.
ki Mrs. Weasley onwongo tye ka cito i Romania me limo Charlie.
I kare ma guweko ot mabuc i agiki me Potions, gunongo yadi ma ki lwongo ni fir madit
yat ma tye ka gengo yoo ma tye anyim. Tyen aryo madongo ma ocung piny
ki dwan malongo owaco bot gi ni Hagrid tye angec ne.
"Apwoyo, Hagrid, imito kony mo?" Ron openyo, kun keto wiye i kin
jange.
"Ku, atye maber, apwoyo, Ron."
