ki angec gi. "Itye ka temo nongo cente mukene, Weasley? Ki gen
me bedo lagwok ler piri keni ka i aa ki i Hogwarts, atamo — ot ma ki yubu ni
Hagrid's omyera onen calo ot ker ka kiporo ki ma jo gang ni gubedo kwede.
Ron odonyo i Malfoy kit ma Snape obino kwede i wi cel.
"WEASLEY!"
Ron oweko nyim bongo pa Malfoy.
"En onongo tye ki akemo, Lapwony Snape," owaco Hagrid, kun keto cinge madit
wang ma tye ki yer woko ki i nge yat. "Malfoy onwongo tye ka buru jo me ode."
