Snape silkily. "Gin abic ki bot Gryffindor, Weasley, ki bed ki pwoc ni pe
mukene bene. Wot anyim, wun weng.
Malfoy, Crabbe, ki Goyle gukato ki i kom yat ni, guket woko
pido kabedo weng ki nyero.
