ki yer wic i Potions.
"Man tye pien ni obedo gin marac atika, me neko ler ma ki lwongo ni unicorn," Firenze owaco.
"Ngat acel keken ma pe ki gin mo me rwenyo, ki gin mo keken me nongo, aye twero timo gin ma kit meno
bal. Remo pa ler ma ki lwongo ni unicorn obi gwoko kwo ni, kadi bed ni itye incit acel ki
too, ento i wel ma lamal. In ineko gin mo maleng ki ma pe ki gwok me
larre keni, ki ibi bedo ki kwo ma romo nucu, kwo ma ki ciko, cake i kare ni
remo ogudo dogi.”
Harry oneno angec pa wic pa Firenze, ma onongo tye ki rangi ryal i
lero dwe.
