Ka twere.
HP 1 - Harry Potter ki
Got pa latim tango
DUL ME APARE 16
I KOT I TRAPDOOR
I mwaka ma tye ka bino, Harry onongo pe obi po kit ma en otimo kwede
me kato ki i peny ne ma en onongo tye ka kuro ni Voldemort obi bino ma opong ki lworo
ki i doggola i cawa mo keken. Ento nino okato, ki onongo pe twero bedo tye
akalakala ni Fluffy onwongo pud kwo ki tye maber i nge doggola ma ki umu ni.
Onwongo lyet tutwal, tutwal i ot kwan madit ma onwongo gi tye iye
waraga gi ma gicoyo. Ki miino gi jami ma pat, manyen pi peny,
ma onongo ki tiyo kwede ki jami me bwola.
Gubedo ki peny me tic bene. Lapwony Flitwick olwongo gi acel acel
ngat acel i kilaci ne me neno ka gi twero timo gin ma ki lwongo ni pineapple tapdance i kom meja.
Lapwony McGonagall oneno gi ka gi loko oyoo me doko bok ma ki lwongo ni snuffbox — points
ki miyo pi kit ma bok ma ki lwongo ni snuffbox ni leng kwede, ento ki kwanyo woko ka onongo tye ki yec.
Snape oweko gin weng gubedo ki lworo, kun yweyo piny i ngut gi nongo gitye ka temo
wi opo kit me yubu yat me wilo jami.
Harry otimo gin maber ma en twero, kun temo kwero arem ma tye ka bino i kome
wic, ma onongo tye ka yello cwinye nicakke i kare ma en ocito i tim.
Neville otamo ni Harry onongo tye ki lworo i kom peny pien Harry onongo pe twero
nino, ento lok ada tye ni Harry onongo tye ka winyo lok marac macon,
kono ni onongo dong rac loyo macon pien onongo tye ngat mo ma oruko bongo i wiye
remo tye ka mol iye.
Twero bedo ni pien onongo pe guneno gin ma Harry oneno i tim,
onyo pien onongo pe ki ret ma lyel i wigi, ento Ron ki
Hermione onongo pe nen calo tye ki par i kom kidi calo Harry. Tam pa
Voldemort owango gi, ento en pi omede ki limo gi i lek, ki
onongo gitye ka tic matek i kwangi ma onongo pe gitye ki kare me paro pire
ngo ma Snape onyo ngat mo keken twero bedo ka timone.
Peny gi me agiki onwongo obedo lok me tekwaro pa jok. Cawa acel me gamo lapeny
lapeny ma mako ludiro macon ma gu yubu jami ma ki lwongo ni cauldrons ki
gubi bedo agonya, labongo cul pi cabit acel maber nio ka adwogi me peny gi obino
woko. I kare ma cwiny pa lapwony Binns owaci gi ni guket jami gi piny ki
guro karatac gi, Harry pi twero juko lok ki jo mukene ni.
"Man onwongo yot loyo kit ma onongo atamo kwede," Hermione owaco ma nongo
odonyo i kin lwak ma onongo gitye ka bino i dye tim ma ceng tye ka ryeny iye. "pe myero abed ka pwonyo
ma mako 1637 Werewolf Code of Conduct onyo lweny pa Elfric the Eager.
Hermione kare weny maro kwano waraga me peny gi ingee kwan, ento
Ron owaco ni man oweko en owinyo marac, ki dong gu cito piny i nam ki gu poto piny
i te yat. Lutino ma ki lwongo ni Weasley twins ki Lee Jordan onwongo tye ka tic ki cinge
rec ma ki lwongo ni squid madit, ma onwongo tye ka yweyo i pii ma lyet. "Pe dong atye ka kwan," Ron
oywak ki yomcwiny, kun ocung i kom lum. "Iromo nen ma yom cwiny,
Harry, wa tye ki cabit acel ma peya wa nongo kit ma wa timo marac kwede, pe tye
myero ibed ki par kombedi."
Harry onwongo tye ka lwoko wiye.
"Amito ni angeyo ngo ma man tere!" en oloko ki akemo. "Arem na tye ka mede
awano — obedo gin ma otimme con, ento pe otimme kare ki kare calo man.
